Chapter 3: Exploratory Data Analysis and Distribution Equality Tests

  1. rusyję wykresy
data <- read.csv("int_data.csv")
dates <- as.Date(data$date, format = "%Y-%m-%d")
alior <- data$closes_alior
ing <- data$closes_ing
plot(
  x = dates,
  y = alior,
  type = "l"
)

plot(
  x = dates,
  y = ing,
  type = "l"
)

hist(
  x = alior,
  freq = FALSE,
  breaks = 30
)

hist(
  x = ing,
  freq = FALSE,
  breaks = 30
)
